nodes.text: The Duel on Corulag was a duel between former Jedi Master Jook-jook H'broozin and his Padawan Danzigorro Potts on Corulag. After H'broozin's fall to the Dark side of the Force and his joining of the Legions of Lettow, he was hunted down continuously by his former Padawan Danzigorro Potts until Potts had cornered him on Corulag where he ran him through, ended the life of his former Master.
